des:
Disclaimer: This skill calls an AI-Generated Parody of Elon Musk!

Speak to a Virtual Elon Musk through your Alexa device. 

The Tesla and SpaceX Boss will interact with you (with your name or any name you give), answer your questions and much more. Ask things like tell me a joke, read Twitter, tell me a fact, tell me the date, ask for help, ask how are you, ask what are you doing, ask what is your name, ask what is your favorite food and more!
